WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.160
1. Be especially careful with the door.

00:05.160 --> 00:09.340
Shut it when you're in and lock it when you go out.

00:09.340 --> 00:16.260
2. I can look after myself, although it won't be easy for me.

00:16.260 --> 00:23.000
3. I'm sure I've forgotten something, but I don't know what it is.

